race.comment: WILL VANSON (8) got around the 350m at this track to take a Free For All in a sharp 19.30 for a 1.5 lengths success. In winning form and can measure up again. WINKING WILLIE (2) comes into this as a quickest on the card winner last time at this track, scoring by a neck (19.22). Looks a primary danger. GOT FLAIR (1) could manage only fifth at this track last time but caught the eye when posting a solid 19.37 over 350m at this track the start prior. Top win two back and can measure up again.  Something for the Multiples: CHEAP RED WINE (4)
